snippet.title: Sonic PC(Sonic PC Port Remake) Luigikid EXE Direct Trailer
snippet.description:
Sonic PC or normally called Sonic PC Port Remake it's our vision about how to make Sonic.exe more interesting, with some gimmicks, better sprite-work, making the gameplay almost like the original games and much more!

Download The Demo Here: https://gamejolt.com/games/PCPORTREMAKE/527553
Luigikid Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCPsV7o0y_il6tF5vhl8fhTQ
